short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Changes the new roblox "charts" back to Discovery.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension changes the controversial (kinda?) change to roblox's discover page. It reverts its name back to the "Discover" page instead of "Charts".

Runs in the background for roblox.com

Built by clue from biitle.nl
